                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7980" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1242</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1609 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">亡羊能否补牢？——基于项目周期的JF地产土地增值税纳税筹划</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Can the dead sheep be mended?- Land Value Added Tax Planning for JF Properties Based on Project Life Cycle</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">赵红，苏瑾，姜翠玲，张莹</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西安交通大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西咸新区紫塬泊汉置业有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">建筑、建材业与房地产业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">房地产企业；土地增值税；纳税筹划；项目生命周期；西部专项</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Real estate companies, Land Value Added Tax, Tax planning, Project lifecycle</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">JF地产成立于2004年，是伴随着西安城市规模扩大和经济发展成长起来的优质房地产开发企业，LX项目是JF地产以项目为主体设立的单独运营的项目公司。纵观现在的房地产行业，行业的利润被压缩，企业进行内部成本的优化迫在眉睫。纳税筹划的专业性和政策性较强，并且之前没有得到足够的重视，JF地产各个部门之间并未培养在项目生命周期的各个关键节点进行土地增值税纳税筹划的意识，纳税筹划的推行存在很大的困难。JF地产的土地增值税纳税筹划往往集中在财务部门的清算阶段，此时产品、销售和成本已基本固定，影响土地增值纳税筹划的效果。本案例基于税务筹划的视角，针对JF地产在房产开发过程中所遇到的土地增值税问题进行探究，着重剖析各税法条文中的相关优惠政策，寻找生命周期下各个阶段的最优纳税筹划方案。案例旨在引导学生理解和学习土地增值税的概念、扣除项目的归属，以及认识房地产开发企业土地增值税的清算条件和方法，从而掌握纳税筹划的基本思路。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Founded in 2004, JF Properties is a high-quality real estate development enterprise that has grown up along with the expansion of Xi&#39;an&#39;s urban scale and economic development. LX Project is a separately operated project company established by JF Properties with the project as the main body. Throughout the real estate industry nowadays, the profit of the industry is compressed, and it is imminent for enterprises to carry out internal cost optimisation. Tax planning is highly professional and policy-oriented and has not been given sufficient attention before, and JF Properties has not cultivated the awareness of land value-added tax planning at various key points in the life cycle of the project among various departments, which makes the implementation of tax planning very difficult. And value-added tax planning of JF Properties is often concentrated in the clearing stage of the finance department, when the products, sales and costs are basically fixed, affecting the land value-added tax planning. At this time, the products, sales and costs have been basically fixed, which affects the effect of land value-added tax planning. Based on the perspective of tax planning, this case explores the land value-added tax (LVAT) issues encountered by JF Properties in the process of property development, focusing on the analysis of the relevant preferential policies in the tax laws, and looking for the optimal tax planning solutions for each stage of the life cycle. The case aims to guide students to understand the concept of land value-added tax, the attribution of deductible items, and the conditions and methods of land value-added tax settlement for real estate development enterprises, so as to master the basic ideas of tax planning..</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《税务筹划》、《中国税制》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">项目生命周期理论；纳税筹划原则；土地增值税税收规定</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-12</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
